(i) Arousing social consciousness regarding distribution of essential commodities;
(ii) Management of public distribution system and constant supervision for making it efficient and transparent. (28) Management of Child Development Programme. (29) Enlarging Cooperative activities -
(i) Management of cooperative - based agriculture, dairy, pisciculture and forest and environment programmes;
(ii) Encouragement to cooperative - based handicraft, handloom, tasar, lac and Malwari production. (iii) Development of Cooperative marketing system.

